   }

Prompt 4 — Correlation matrix
Mam market_data_adapter.py i performance_metrics.py.

Stwórz backend/services/analytics/correlation_service.py:

1. calculate_correlation_matrix(tickers: list[str], period: str = "1y") → dict
   - używa market_data_adapter.get_historical_returns()
   - Pearson correlation między wszystkimi parami
   {
     "recharts_data": [{"symbol": "AAPL", "AAPL": 1.0, "MSFT": 0.87},...],
     "high_correlation_pairs": [{"pair": ["AAPL","MSFT"], "correlation": 0.87},...],
     "avg_correlation": float,
     "period": str
   }
   recharts_data musi być zgodne z recharts heatmap (lista obiektów)

2. portfolio_correlation_risk(portfolio_id: int,
                               sub_portfolio_id: int = None) → dict
   - pobiera tickers z holdings (ten portfolio_id)
   - identyfikuje klastry mocno skorelowanych aktywów (threshold > 0.75)
   {
     "avg_correlation": float,
     "risk_level": "low" | "medium" | "high",
     "clusters": [["AAPL", "MSFT", "GOOGL"], ["XOM", "CVX"]],
     "high_correlation_pairs": [...],
     "recommendation": str
   }

WAŻNE: portfolio ma sub-portfele. Jeśli sub_portfolio_id=None, 
zbierz tickers ze wszystkich sub-portfeli tego portfolio_id.

Prompt 5 — Diversification Score
Mam serwisy analytics.

Stwórz backend/services/analytics/diversification_service.py:

1. herfindahl_index(weights: list[float]) → float
   HHI = Σ(wi²), weights muszą sumować się do 1.0

2. diversification_score(portfolio_id: int, 
                           sub_portfolio_id: int = None) → dict
   - pobiera holdings z market_data_adapter.get_holdings_snapshot()
   - snapshot ma już wagi (value-based)
   - grupuje też by sector (kolumna sector w holdings — może być None)
   {
     "hhi": float,
     "score": int,              # 0-100 (100 = idealna dywersyfikacja)
     "rating": "poor"|"fair"|"good"|"excellent",
     "by_asset": [
       {"ticker": str, "weight": float, "sector": str, "hhi_contribution": float}
     ],
     "by_sector": [
       {"sector": str, "weight": float, "hhi_contribution": float}
     ],
     "top_concentration_warning": str | None,
     "recommendation": str
   }

Progi: HHI>0.25 poor(0-40), 0.15-0.25 fair(40-65), 0.05-0.15 good(65-85), <0.05 excellent(85-100)
Jeśli sektor = None lub "" → grupuj jako "Nieznany"

